[3] China (LC)
Date: Thu 23 May 2013
Source: Lanzhou Evening News [In Chinese, machine translation, not edited - Mod.CP]
http://www.kaixian.tv/R1/n2651494c7.shtml

Measles outbreak in Longnan city
--------------------------------
Since late March this year [2013], Wudu District reported abnormal increase in reported cases of measles, the incidence was significantly higher than last year [2012]. The Chinese Center for Disease Control, the provincial health department investigation team conducted a field survey and found Longnan measles prevention and control work in the existence of class measles vaccination is not solid, does not take the initiative to deal with the epidemic and other serious problems. 22 May 2013, Gansu Provincial Health Department has conducted some criticism.

According to "China Disease Prevention and Control Information System" report,
1 Jan.-11 May 2013 report current address for the JCP Wudu District, 111 cases of suspected cases of measles, including laboratory diagnosis of 88 cases, an outbreak of measles; Longnan City People's Hospital and the Hospital of Wudu District, the largest number of reported cases, 2 hospitals reported cases accounted for Wudu Chief cases of 88.99%. The epidemic is mainly younger age children and adult-onset, in which case 0-2 years and 15 years of age accounted for 95.41% of the total cases. The investigation team field for measles vaccination rate class rapid assessment results show:

1. Measles Vaccine 2 surveys vaccination immunization rate was 47.83%.
2.March 2013 supplementary immunization survey vaccination rate 79.07%.

3 surveyed villages exist in card, cards, inconsistent registered on the phenomenon.

Investigation Group agreed that the main reason for the outbreak of the epidemic are:
1- basic immunization of measles vaccine working class is weak. Survey measles vaccine 2 times vaccination class rate, not a solid basis for immunization, management is not standardized, there is population immunity gaps, increasing the spread of measles in the crowd danger. Health administrative departments at all levels for measles prevention and control work seriously enough, poor supervision work, the lack of effective training of junior officers.

2- hospital infection control efforts ineffective. According to epidemiological analysis of the survey shows that the spread of measles Wudu District, one of the main cross-infection control in hospitals is missing, cases of mismanagement, the emergence of the epidemic in the early failed to take timely and effective prevention and control measures to deal with Measles outbreaks spread triggered.

3- strong sense of infectious diseases. Suspected measles cases omission is serious, infectious disease management department medical institutions active search and did not carry out active surveillance of nosocomial, hospital clinicians suspected cases of measles reporting requirements for low awareness.

4- fever clinics and triage system implementation is not in place. Medical institutions did not conduct triage fever cases, suspected cases of measles have not implemented the 1st diagnosis responsibility system for the treatment of suspected cases did not take timely and appropriate quarantine disposal, sampling and basic information on the registration, resulting in cases of lost, increasing the the risk of epidemic spread.

Gansu Provincial Health Department instructed the Municipal Health Bureau, according to the "major mistake in Gansu Province vaccination accountability measures (Trial)" and "accountability, Gansu Province Hospital Infection Management Measures (Trial)" on the responsible units and persons responsible for accountability and Responsibility will handle the situation on 15 June [2013] in writing of the provincial health department.

(By Tian Xiaodong)

