[This [basically] unaltered machine translation provides an insight into the prevalence of measles in China and the the organisation of vaccination responses. Longnan City is situated in the southeast of Gansu Province, neighboring Shaanxi Province in the east and Sichuan Province in the south. Within Gansu, Longnan borders Tianshui in the north and Gannan Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture in the west. - Mod.CP]

