[4] Pakistan (Punjab)
Date: Mon 20 May 2013
Source: Pakistan Today [edited]
http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2013/05/20/city/lahore/death-toll-hits-90-as-3-more-succumb-to-measles/


Death toll hits 90 as 3 more succumb to measles
-----------------------------------------------
3 children died of measles on Monday [20 May 2013] bringing the overall death toll in Punjab to 90 since January [2013]. The deceased children were undergoing treatment in Children's Hospital Lahore. 9000 children were affected by measles in Punjab, rousing the provincial health authorities to launch a children's vaccination week between 24-30 April[2013]. However the measles outbreak has still not been controlled, causing deaths across the country.

